</div>From what other games have done: Rested XP is a buff that gives bonus to xp gained.  The duration of the buff builds up the longer you don't adventure with that character.<br />
<br />
Power gamers see little benefit.<br />
<br />
Crafters, those with limited play time and folks that jump between alts get to see noticeable progress when they do work on adventuring.<br />
<br />
It will benefit my wife so I am all for it. :D</div>
