		<div align="left" style="font-size: 12px; color: #999999; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">You can't lose a level as it is now.<br />
The rested xp thing sounds similar to what they have in EQ2. If it is then I don't think it will be much of an issue, I barely even noticed the mechanic, though I did know a few people that when the bonus dropped to 0% they would log out because they felt they were no longer playing efficiently or some such nonsense.<br />
I still say these changes are not to make the game more like WoW but more like EQ2, which I guess, is almost as bad.</div>
